lead_paragraph: Wallabies flyhalf Quade Cooper has signed a three-year contract with the Australian Rugby Union and the Queensland Reds, confirming his return after a season with French club Toulon.

headline.print_headline: Cooper Confirms Three-Year Deal With Wallabies, Queensland
headline.main: Cooper Confirms Three-Year Deal With Wallabies, Queensland
